name: Flipping-form
tagline: A 3D flipping form css plugin to bring your forms to life and to help encourage people to enter their details... hopefully!
body:
#Flippin 3D form.

Cool little form which reveals a input field when hovered using 3d animation.

![Screenshot](https://github.com/kevinrodrigues/flipping-form/img/screenshot.gif "Screenshot")
